listings.title: Kioti 50hp Tractor with Grapple
listings.description: 2016 DK5010 4x4 tractor. 50hp Kioti KL5510 loader. 72 inch bucket with 2,660lb lift capacity. 72 inch skid steer mount root grapple. 8x8 shuttle shift. Quick attach loader with skid steer bucket. Tilt steering. Cruise PTO. 1 set of remote hydraulics.
